    <h2>Adjustments for Convergences:</h2>
    <p class="caution">note: Power builds benefit from the items below, while others do not. Therefore, it is recommended to bring a power build to convergences.</p>

    
    <h3>
        <image src="/images/SotO/Secrets_of_the_Obscure_logo.png" alt="SotO Logo" style="width:75px;" />
        <image src="/images/JW/Janthir_Wilds_logo.png" alt="JW Logo" style="width:75px;" />
        SotO and JW items
    </h3>
    
    <p>
        These items work in both SotO and JW convergences.
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>
            <h4>
                <image src="https://render.guildwars2.com/file/7A9EA9E0C702F8BA595973FED3A853646B2E07F8/222720.png" alt="potion of demon slaying" style="width:50px;"/>
                <a href="https://wiki.guildwars2.com/wiki/Powerful_Potion_of_Demon_Slaying" target="_blank">Powerful Potion of Demon Slaying</a>
            </h4>
            <p>
                (1 hour): 10% Damage vs. Demons, Kryptis, and Titanspawn. -10% Damage from Demons, Kryptis, and Titanspawn.
            </p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <h4>
                <image src="https://render.guildwars2.com/file/991BD2CC63CFE343C5E55D49F657C95E71FD0439/340600.png" alt="sigil of demon slaying" style="width:50px;"/>
                <a href="https://wiki.guildwars2.com/wiki/Superior_Sigil_of_Demon_Slaying" target="_blank">Superior Sigil of Demon Slaying</a>
            </h4>
            <p>
                3% Strike Damage, +7% Strike Damage vs. Demons, Kryptis, and Titanspawn. Totals to 10% Strike Damage when satisfied.
            </p>
        </li>
        <li>
            
            <h4><image src="https://render.guildwars2.com/file/DFF4EB43AD0803F60D105658052321A0BE1AF02C/3592832.png" alt="eagle relic" style="width:50px;" />
                <a href="https://wiki.guildwars2.com/wiki/Relic_of_the_Eagle" target="_blank">Relic of the Eagle</a>
            </h4>
            <p>
                10% damage when enemy under 50% hp. 
            </p>
            <p>
                Swap to Eagle when transitioning to the third boss phase (start of 50%).
            </p>
        </li>
    </ul>

    <p>
        Consider taking a <a href="https://wiki.guildwars2.com/wiki/Sigil#Stacking_bonus" target="_blank">stacking sigil</a> to convergences. They're easy to build up during the phases before the boss spawns.
    </p>

